article_text:
Today

A mix of clouds and sun. A stray shower or thunderstorm is possible. High near 85F. Winds WNW at 10 to 15 mph.

Tonight

Partly cloudy. Low 57F. Winds SW at 5 to 10 mph.

Tomorrow

Partly cloudy early. Scattered thunderstorms developing in the afternoon. High 86F. Winds S at 5 to 10 mph. Chance of rain 40%.
